00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:52,180
=Gorgeous Dream=
(Adapted from the novel "The Charming Evil Consort.")

2
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:55,020
=Episode 4=

3
00:00:57,612 --> 00:00:58,733
Father, Mother, I hope you are well.

4
00:00:59,212 --> 00:01:01,172
May I know why you have summoned I?

5
00:01:02,133 --> 00:01:04,652
You forged your household records
to infiltrate the Liu Residence.

6
00:01:05,173 --> 00:01:06,333
What was your intention?

7
00:01:09,693 --> 00:01:10,452
I am slow-witted,

8
00:01:10,932 --> 00:01:12,973
and do not understand what Mother means.

9
00:01:14,012 --> 00:01:14,652
Come in.

10
00:01:25,973 --> 00:01:27,812
I am Cuixian of the Lianxiang Pavilion.

11
00:01:28,012 --> 00:01:31,493
I greet Master Liu and Madam Liu.

12
00:01:45,732 --> 00:01:48,253
Is this not my dear sister Si?

13
00:01:50,372 --> 00:01:51,292
Si.

14
00:01:51,973 --> 00:01:53,173
You are a courtesan,

15
00:01:54,053 --> 00:01:55,852
yet you dared disguise yourself
as a common woman,

16
00:01:55,973 --> 00:01:57,253
and entered the Liu Residence as a maid.

17
00:01:57,973 --> 00:01:59,732
You truly are bold.

18
00:02:02,773 --> 00:02:03,533
Master, Madam,

19
00:02:03,652 --> 00:02:04,572
I do not know this woman.

20
00:02:08,372 --> 00:02:09,173
Si,

21
00:02:09,532 --> 00:02:10,532
you changed your name,

22
00:02:10,550 --> 00:02:12,090
and now you pretend
not to know your own sister?

23
00:02:14,053 --> 00:02:16,893
If you had not harmed
that patron back then,

24
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,360
how would I have been
dragged down with you,

25
00:02:18,372 --> 00:02:19,532
beaten until I was covered in wounds?

26
00:02:19,652 --> 00:02:20,613
Have you forgotten all that?

27
00:02:21,573 --> 00:02:22,053
Get up.

28
00:02:25,412 --> 00:02:26,132
Father, Mother,

29
00:02:26,670 --> 00:02:28,613
Huan Xi entered the Liu Residence
with me after I married in.

30
00:02:28,853 --> 00:02:29,812
That makes her one of us.

31
00:02:30,532 --> 00:02:31,652
How could you believe the words

32
00:02:32,013 --> 00:02:33,773
of someone who slanders
without evidence?

33
00:02:34,972 --> 00:02:35,773
Master, Madam,

34
00:02:36,252 --> 00:02:38,333
this little wench
has a red mole on her shoulder,

35
00:02:38,652 --> 00:02:40,493
it is what the patrons liked the most.

36
00:02:41,053 --> 00:02:42,372
I will let you all see it now.

37
00:02:42,412 --> 00:02:43,092
What are you doing?

38
00:02:44,812 --> 00:02:46,812
Young Master Liu, you are here.

39
00:02:49,493 --> 00:02:50,773
I am Cuixian.

40
00:02:51,293 --> 00:02:52,092
Quite lively in here.

41
00:02:56,613 --> 00:02:57,532
Do you still recall

42
00:02:57,573 --> 00:02:59,613
the Si who served you together with me?

43
00:03:00,812 --> 00:03:02,493
It is her. Do you recognize her?

44
00:03:10,453 --> 00:03:11,013
I do not.

45
00:03:11,493 --> 00:03:11,932
Qing.

46
00:03:12,132 --> 00:03:12,972
Come, have some tea.

47
00:03:14,812 --> 00:03:17,333
(Huan Xi served in Lianxiang Pavilion
with her face veiled.)

48
00:03:17,733 --> 00:03:18,690
(She should not be recognized.)

49
00:03:18,932 --> 00:03:20,212
Young Master Liu, look.

50
00:03:21,333 --> 00:03:22,453
The red mole on her shoulder.

51
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:23,773
One glance is enough to recognize her.

52
00:03:23,773 --> 00:03:24,493
Let go.

53
00:03:26,893 --> 00:03:27,573
I recognize it.

54
00:03:39,053 --> 00:03:39,692
I recognize it.

55
00:03:40,252 --> 00:03:40,932
I recognize her.

56
00:03:42,333 --> 00:03:43,132
Master, Madam,

57
00:03:43,252 --> 00:03:43,812
you see,

58
00:03:44,013 --> 00:03:45,092
was I not right?

59
00:03:45,372 --> 00:03:47,173
This little wench sneaked
into the Liu Residence

60
00:03:47,493 --> 00:03:48,773
with ulterior motives.

61
00:03:49,453 --> 00:03:50,613
It appears that Lou's death

62
00:03:50,733 --> 00:03:52,053
has something to do with her.

63
00:03:52,692 --> 00:03:54,053
She is only a maid.

64
00:03:54,173 --> 00:03:55,773
She could never do all this alone.

65
00:03:55,972 --> 00:03:57,412
There must be

66
00:03:59,573 --> 00:04:01,013
someone behind her.

67
00:04:20,173 --> 00:04:20,733
All of this

68
00:04:21,772 --> 00:04:22,413
was done by me.

69
00:04:22,572 --> 00:04:23,653
I am the one who killed Lou.

70
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:26,080
Every one of you in the Liu Residence
pretends to be virtuous,

71
00:04:26,093 --> 00:04:27,252
yet all of you are filthy and corrupt.

72
00:04:27,533 --> 00:04:28,932
Hypocrites and venomous snakes.

73
00:04:29,053 --> 00:04:29,973
Steeped in wickedness.

74
00:04:30,173 --> 00:04:32,493
And you, drugging yourself, drinking,
and playing with women.

75
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:32,892
Steward Chen!

76
00:04:32,892 --> 00:04:34,093
- None of you deserve a good end!
- Get out!

77
00:04:34,733 --> 00:04:35,613
I will do whatever I want.

78
00:04:35,613 --> 00:04:36,132
Huan Xi.

79
00:04:36,533 --> 00:04:36,892
Wenyu.

80
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:37,812
- Who do you think you are?
- Huan Xi!

81
00:04:37,812 --> 00:04:38,213
Wenyu.

82
00:04:38,213 --> 00:04:39,012
Who do you think you are?

83
00:04:40,733 --> 00:04:41,012
Huan Xi.

84
00:04:41,012 --> 00:04:42,853
Shameless creature.

85
00:04:43,173 --> 00:04:43,812
- Let go.
- Are you hurt?

86
