90
00:04:49,533 --> 00:04:50,973
Speak. Who instructed you?

91
00:04:52,213 --> 00:04:52,812
Huan Xi.

92
00:04:54,012 --> 00:04:54,812
Huan Xi, your hand.

93
00:04:55,372 --> 00:04:55,932
Get away.

94
00:04:56,653 --> 00:04:57,613
You foolish woman.

95
00:04:59,173 --> 00:05:00,252
I used you.

96
00:05:00,853 --> 00:05:03,692
I returned solely for revenge.

97
00:05:06,132 --> 00:05:07,012
Huan Xi.

98
00:05:08,772 --> 00:05:09,372
Huan Xi.

99
00:05:15,173 --> 00:05:16,733
I will make every one of you

100
00:05:17,093 --> 00:05:18,493
pay for blood with blood.

101
00:05:18,493 --> 00:05:19,812
Are you looking for death?

102
00:05:19,812 --> 00:05:20,332
Let go of me.

103
00:05:20,332 --> 00:05:20,772
Huan Xi.

104
00:05:20,892 --> 00:05:21,932
- Let go of me.
- Do you want to die?

105
00:05:22,772 --> 00:05:23,932
Huan Xi!

106
00:05:25,372 --> 00:05:26,213
Drag her to the woodshed.

107
00:05:26,613 --> 00:05:28,493
She will be executed at noon tomorrow.

108
00:05:31,932 --> 00:05:32,653
Huan Xi!

109
00:05:33,653 --> 00:05:34,772
Huan Xi!

110
00:05:54,132 --> 00:05:55,012
With your kind heart,

111
00:05:55,613 --> 00:05:56,812
you will surely save her.

112
00:06:00,613 --> 00:06:04,132
Shen Wanqing.

113
00:06:18,493 --> 00:06:19,613
Xie Ruilan.

114
00:06:21,252 --> 00:06:22,653
Xie Ruilan.

115
00:06:57,053 --> 00:06:57,493
Sir.

116
00:07:00,973 --> 00:07:02,173
Please, help me save Huan Xi.

117
