124
00:07:15,372 --> 00:07:16,533
Only by toppling them

125
00:07:16,533 --> 00:07:17,853
can we get close to the truth.

126
00:07:18,252 --> 00:07:18,812
I

127
00:07:19,293 --> 00:07:21,932
