this three years ago.

134
00:07:54,413 --> 00:07:55,772
When the enemy is difficult to face,

135
00:07:56,692 --> 00:07:57,932
one must lower oneself,

136
00:07:59,053 --> 00:08:02,053
to strike when least expected.

137
00:08:05,213 --> 00:08:06,853
You stayed in
the Liu Residence these days.

138
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:08,973
You must have something
on the Xie family.

139
00:08:10,812 --> 00:08:11,733
If you want to live,

140
