never tell anyone

143
00:08:22,012 --> 00:08:23,812
that I trained you.

144
00:08:26,812 --> 00:08:27,853
I only need to deal with you.

145
00:08:31,813 --> 00:08:32,453
Master Xie.

146
00:08:33,012 --> 00:08:33,532
Farewell.

147
00:08:39,213 --> 00:08:40,573
You are not poisoned.

148
00:08:41,333 --> 00:08:42,813
Compared to three years ago,

149
00:08:43,493 --> 00:08:44,693
she has gained a sharper edge.

150
00:08:47,652 --> 00:08:48,412
Lan Mengyan.

151
00:08:49,573 --> 00:08:50,733
I shall see for myself

152
00:08:51,252 --> 00:08:52,292
how this blade of yours

153
00:08:53,493 --> 00:08:55,093
will draw blood.

154
00:09:13,532 --> 00:09:14,093
Useless fool.

155
00:09:15,292 --> 00:09:18,252
(Xie Yaozu grew up
steeped in male supremacy.)

156
00:09:18,892 --> 00:09:21,613
(Now he must live under his sister's
shadow in the Liu household.)

157
00:09:23,132 --> 00:09:24,652
(Resentment churns within him.)

158
00:09:25,213 --> 00:09:26,733
(And he vents it upon the weak.)

159
00:09:28,813 --> 00:09:30,813
Do you think you are even convincing?

160
00:09:34,532 --> 00:09:35,772
Xie Yaozu, you useless fool.

161
00:09:36,172 --> 00:09:37,693
You cannot handle the smallest task.

162
00:09:38,973 --> 00:09:40,052
Hurry up and go.

163
00:09:42,933 --> 00:09:43,493
Continue.

164
00:09:43,733 --> 00:09:44,213
Useless.

165
00:09:45,093 --> 00:09:47,853
You cannot even
manage something so trivial.

166
00:09:48,012 --> 00:09:48,532
Continue.

167
00:09:48,772 --> 00:09:49,733
If not for me,

168
00:09:50,372 --> 00:09:52,132
