180
00:10:10,853 --> 00:10:11,973
How dare you?

181
00:10:12,813 --> 00:10:13,813
Xie Zhaodi.

182
00:10:14,333 --> 00:10:16,453
Did you really think a new name
could change your fate?

183
00:10:16,493 --> 00:10:19,213
You are nothing but a lowly thing
warming Liu Qinghe's bed.

184
00:10:21,573 --> 00:10:22,412
Do not forget

185
00:10:22,813 --> 00:10:24,973
